{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-09e_049", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre VI"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", quartier de juillet 1678 (tome III), p. 49-52."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "LETTRE VI."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il y a quelques temps, Monsieur, que je me mets sur le pied de bel Esprit, c’est à dire de bel Esprit de Province, & personne ne s’estoit encore avisé de m’en disputer le Titre, que dans une Compagnie où je me trouvay hier apres dîné. Je tâchois là de debiter mes Fleuretes à demy-fletries entre cinq ou six Belles, & je me faisois attentivement écouter par deux ou trois Sots qui se récrimoient à chaque parole, quand un nouveau venu, lequel apparament n’avoit pas accoûtumé de demeurer sans rien dire, ennuyé de m’entendre toûjours parler, & se fâchant de me voir trop applaudy ; Mon Dieu ! Dit-il, il semble que Monsieur est icy quelque Oracle ; il veut faire le bel Esprit, & son nom n’est point dans le Mercure. Je vous avoüe, Monsieur, que ce reproche me toucha. Je sortis brusquement sans répondre une parole, & j’allay chercher un Mercure, avec lequel je me vins enfermer dans mon Cabinet, où apres avoir vû vos Enigmes avec attention, j’invoquay plus de six fois Apollon & les Muses, lesquelles m’inspirerent ces pensées."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce petit Nain avec son gros teignon,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui d’un pied vient en diligence,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et comme un rude Compagnon"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut terrasser un Homme d’importance,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Sçavez-vous bien ce que j’en pense ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce n’est ma foy qu’un"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Champignon."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans tant tourner autour du pot,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour trouver de ces Vers le veritable Mot,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu'à deviner chacun s’appreste,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne me dis pas grand Prophete,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais c’est"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " la Barbe"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": ", ou je ne suis qu’un Sot."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu'il est doux de s’imaginer"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce que dans ce Tableau cette Enigme nous marque !"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "C'est le fruit des travaux de nostre grand Monarque,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "C'est "}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "la Paix "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "que LOUIS s’appreste à nous donner."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres cela, Monsieur, je demeureray fort satisfait de moy, & je pris bien dessein de me vanger de l’Homme qui m’avoit méprisé, en luy faisant voir dans la premier Mercure, entre les autres noms imprimez, celuy de vostre tres-humble serviteur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Y. Z."}]}]}]}